  • Classes in edu.vt.api.eatstreet.model.menu used by edu.vt.api.eatstreet.model.menu 
    Class and Description
    Customization
    This model class represents a customization that can be made to an item on a restaurant's menu (a MenuItem object).
    CustomizationChoice
    This model class represents a possible choice that can be made for a particular menu item's customization For example: Customization - Add Black Olives To Pizza CustomizationChoice - On Half of Pizza CustomizationChoice - On All of Pizza
    CustomizationGroup
    This model class represents a group of particular customizations that can be made to a menu item.
    MenuItem
    This model class represents an item on a restaurant's menu.
